title: CAKE distribution to early users of PancakeSwap
body:
PancakeSwap is becoming extremely popular nowadays, but this wouldn't happen if not us: the early users of the platform, the people who believed in this project from the beginning, risking our money and our trust. 
Some of us lost such a big part of our investment, others got real punished regarding the SYRUP matter and others simply made the best decisions of our lives. No matter what, we have and deserve the right to be compensated with our beloved CAKE. 

The petition is basically a generous number of CAKE tokens to be sent to each address which have interacted with any contract created by PancakeSwap (that includes swaps, liquidity providers and pool farmers) before the date of November 1st, 2020.

Please, leave your opinion with a vote here, either you agree or disagree. PancakeSwap team must know about this.
choices: Yes, make a CAKE distribution to early users
No, don't make a CAKE distribution to early users
author: 0xc1a03d3Ea213C37e5A86045fFE95096412534025
